videos.headline: Bachmeier hits Hightower for the Boise State TD
videos.description: Hank Bachmeier lofts a touchdown pass to John Hightower to increase Boise State's lead on Hawai'i.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Bachmeier hits Hightower for the Boise State TD) 2019/10/12

videos.headline: Bachmeier loses fumble, leaves with injury
videos.description: Boise State loses more than a fumble after Hank Bachmeier takes a hard hit and exits with an injury.
